     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Tokyo Night theme. Deep blue-night
         background (#1A1B26) with electric blue (#7AA2F7) and magenta (#BB9AF7)
         accents. Inspired by the neon lights of Tokyo at night.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in TokyoNightTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

